      "content": "but that feels like a bit of a leap to say it's \"vastly outweighed\" without actually looking at the numbers. what about the end of life for the turbines? i've heard a lot about them just sitting in landfills because the blades are hard to recycle. shouldn't that be a major part of the comparison?",
